<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="73" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="6" pageNumber="73">Culture characters.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="6" pageNumber="73">On PDA, cultures are initially white, becoming isabelline after 2 weeks. The colonies are flat with irregular edge; texture uniform within 1 month at 25 °C in the dark.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
